Version 0.01
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
Implement some simple useful functions for list which are missed in other packages.
.PP
See also \f(CW\*(C`List::Util\*(C'\fR and \f(CW\*(C`List::MoreUtils\*(C'\fR
.PP
